    • Method Detail

      • createGroup

        Group createGroup(GroupParameters groupParameters)
        Given a GroupParameters object, create a group and save it in the data store. If groupParameters contains a name and a null parent id, then a root type group is created. If groupParameters has both a name and a parent group id then an intermediate type group is created. If the parent group id given is not in the data store then a root group type is created.
        Parameters:
        groupParameters -
        Returns:
        The Group that was created
